                    <h3>Weight vs Stability</h3>
                    <p>Lighter tripods are easier to carry but less stable in wind. Carbon fiber offers the best
                        strength-to-weight ratio but costs more.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Flip Locks vs Twist Locks</h3>
                    <p>Flip/lever locks are faster to adjust. Twist locks are more compact but can freeze in cold
                        weather or get grit in them.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Head Matters</h3>
